        <p class="hero-eyebrow">The Stress-Proof Adaptogen</p>
        <p>Rhodiola Rosea is an arctic root used for centuries in Russia and Scandinavia by soldiers, climbers, and laborers to keep working through cold, altitude, and exhaustion. Modern research has made it one of the most studied adaptogens in the world.</p>
        <p>Adaptogens are a defined category of plants that help the body maintain balance under stress. Rhodiola is the one with the deepest research record for mental endurance and fatigue resistance under demand.</p>
      </div>
