        <h2>Why We Use It</h2>
        <p>Rhodiola is the ingredient in DayShift built for the third hour of focused work, the fifth meeting, the afternoon slump. It supports the body's stress response so mental energy holds up when the day keeps going.</p>
        <p>250 mg per packet, standardized for salidroside and rosavin, dosed within the clinically studied range for stress and cognitive endurance.</p>
